snippet.textDisplay:
Young Desi Rap Verses] 
Band wagon munday saray karday jo pailay hoya Kadday nain ganay par sunda ni moya leh dass Dud patti chaa naal rass Y’all ain’t messin with us I’m a one man army.
 Asli aan desi nalay baki saray farmi I alone am authentic, 
everyone else is generic I do it for my city I do it for my Pind, 
Sarson da tail, 
Gilli Gilli tind Jivain larda ey foji,
 meri camouflage dhoti Dawan thallay manji nalay, 
Khawan bay k roti Gallan karday nain choti Munday janday ni hunay Young Desi. Pullaya ni Culture, 
Anday wala burger Sohni kardi ey harkat Chaldi ey jadun mallay pay jaandi barkat circus Din poora aye na sakoon mainu, 
Raat sari kuriyan day phone mainu Boldi nain javin na tu bhool mainu, 
Call back karin tu zaroor mainu Sohni DM kardi fazool mainu Models kardiyan phone mainu, 
Boldi ain video ch rakh lay qabool mainu Unj e dalair nalay kuch mairay genetics, 
Money on my mind they call me a fanatic, 
Bol mairay jivain jaadu karay koi magician, 
Sohniyai ni tu ki janay mera ki ambition King of my city Meri chaldi permission, Bar Bar Phuchday nain maira hun, 
hey! Sir Sir bolday nain saray hun Tu hands ni mera maazi Lawan kalabazi, 
Raazi,
 Lay gaya may baazi, 
Rab raazi, 
Baki munday saray marday nain bongi,
 Gallan karda may taazi, 
Munday phuchday nain baray mairay, 
Tell em I’m a one man army, 
I’m a one man army -x2, 123, 
pawain burger khaa pawain lassi pee Tainu masla ki, 
Ey munday saray nain banday nain rapper, 
Taun thallay sat maran phar k may vapar Burger ketchup, 
putha sidda kardain nain getup, 
Darday nain ey saray khaanday homeopathic, 
Waikhdi ey mainu sohni sailiyan nu Maray koni salaiyan nu Kaindi phiray swag idda check kar Munday sunday nain ganay mairay Rokday nain gaddi nalay bolday nain Mundayan nu chaiti Young Desi aala gaana fir back kar. 
Shekho Young Desi aya Siddi puttay maari thaapi, 
Munda poora paapi, 
Nalay chitta kaala laynga Uttun chakkaya gandaasa Jera Nooray aakhay kharkay May pan daini naasan Lay main lahori munda shehri Phichun pind Narowal. 
Nazreen Shair apni kataab Listeners, the poet in his book Swag or uskay Abaoajdaad’ Swag and it’s ancestors’ Mein kehta hai keh, Umray rafta lot’ti nahin keh Mujhay anday wala burger mangaa do. 
Yan soday wali botal pala do, 
Kay yehi hay janoonay ishq ki intayhaa. 
Keekli kaleer di, 
Pag mairay veer di Dupatta mairay pai daa Fittay mu jawae daae. 
Sohni takdi ey Swag mera, 
Sadqay may javaan tera gora gora rang maiya, 
Pent teri ponchayan tou tang maiya Munday saray teray phichay chir gaye aa jang maiya. 
Lyallpur mairay yaar bhaitay
